      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Dis atgreeſahs winnam pakak ne darriu. Buhtu es dſehris fo\n(tohs Wenaidneekus) ap-\nlaupiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Pehz winnu bija Sam-\nnus/ Aga Dehls tas Arariteris.\nRad tee Wilisteri bij faputzejschees\nweenâ Zeemâ/ un tur bija weens\nTihruus ar Lehzahm / un tee\nLaudts behdse preekſch teem Wi-\nliftereem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Tad apſtahjebs wiꞥſch\npacha Tihruma Widdû / un\npahrſtahweja to / un kawe tohs\nWilisterus/ un tas KUNGS de-\nwe leeſu Pestischanit.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Un ſchee trihs Wirfneeki\nſtarp trihsdesmits angſteem Wiḫ-\nreem/ nogahje / un nahze Vtau-\njama Laikâ pee Dahwida/ Adul-\nlama Alla/ un to Wilistern Pul-\nki bij apinettuschees eekſch tahs\nCeletjas Rewaim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "14. Bet Dahwids bija to\nBrihdi kahdâ Stiprumâ/ un tee\nWilistext bij Betlemê Karra-\nWihrus likkutchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "15. Un Dahwids ſahze eekah-\nrotees/ un ſazzija: Kas dohs man\nUhdeni dsert no tahs Akkas/ kas\neekſch Betlemes Wahrtim irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "16. Tad lausahs tchee trihs\nWarrenee zaur to Wilistern Leh-\ngeri/ un finehle Uhdeni no Bet-\nlemes Akkas/ kas Wahrtis bija/\nun nehme/ un atneffe to pee Dah-\nwida. Bet wiꞥſch ne gribbeja to\ndsert / bet islehje to preekſch ta\nKUNGA /\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "17. Un ſazzija: Lai tas KUNGS\nmann no ta pafarga / ka es to\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wibru Affint/ kas nogahju-\nfawu Dſihwibu ne taupidam\nun wiꞥſch ne gribbeja to dſe\nScho darrija ſchee trihs We-\nrenee.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Abisajns/ Joaba Bra-\nlis/ Zerujas Dehls/ bija arri p\nWirfneeku/ ſtarp trim. Tas p\nzehle fawu Schkehpu prett tri-\nſimteem/ un nokawe tohs / wi-\nwiꞥſch bija arridsan flaweſt\nſtarp teem trim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. No teem trim bija wi-\ntas augſtaſaajs/tavehz bija wi-\nteem par Wirfneeku/bet wiꞥſch\npanahze tohs trihs (pirmajus\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Wehl bija Benajus/ J-\njada Dehls / weena stipra Wi-\nra Dehls / kas leeſus Darb-\ndarrijs/ no Kabzeëles / ſchis kar-\ndivi stiprius Moabitezu Lauwa-\nwiꞥſch arri nogahje / un kar-\nweenu Lauwu weenâ Alla Sne-\ngu Laikâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "21. Wiꞥſch arri kawe wee-\nEgiptern breeſtignu Wibru / ta Egiptera Rohkâ bija wee-\nSchkehps / bet wiꞥſch nogah-\npee ta ar weenu Sisli/ un iſra-\nwe to Schkehpu no ta Egipte-\nRohkas/ un nokawe to ar fan-\npatchu Schkehpu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "22. Scho darrija Benaju-\nJojada Dehls / un wiꞥſch bi-\nflawehts ſtarp teem trim Wa-\nreneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "23. Wiꞥſch bija tas augſ-\nkajs ſtarp teem trihsdesmiteen-\nbet tohs trihs pirmajus wiꞥſch-\npana-\n"
    }
